# Deliberately NOT excluding node_modules/** here: vsce ships production
# `dependencies` (vscode-languageclient + its transitive deps) and prunes
# `devDependencies` (@types/*, typescript, @vscode/vsce) automatically —
# verified via `npx vsce ls`. A blanket `node_modules/**` exclude would drop
# vscode-languageclient too and silently break the LSP client at runtime.
**/.DS_Store
